I JUST TALKED TO HIM.

28:22.201 --> 28:23.869
YEAH, IT'S PROBABLY

28:22.201 --> 28:23.869
THE TERRORIST.

28:23.910 --> 28:25.871
I DON'T THINK SO, MA'AM.

28:25.912 --> 28:28.207
IN HOMELAND,

28:25.912 --> 28:28.207
WE AREN'T PAID TO THINK.

28:28.248 --> 28:29.875
WE'RE PAID TO ACT.

28:29.916 --> 28:32.169
COMMENCE ZULU DELTA

28:29.916 --> 28:32.169
ON MY MARK...

28:33.920 --> 28:36.632
OKAY, DELTA TEAM, LET'S GO.

28:36.674 --> 28:39.426
KEEP YOUR HEAD DOWN.

28:36.674 --> 28:39.426
THEY'RE COMING IN.

28:49.019 --> 28:51.689
[ Whispering ] 3, 2, 1.

28:51.730 --> 28:55.192
[ GLASS SHATTERS, POPPING ]

28:57.528 --> 29:00.280
PULL BACK! PULL BACK!

29:03.158 --> 29:04.910
WELCOME TO THE PARTY, PAL.

29:04.951 --> 29:07.204
I DON'T KNOW WHO YOU ARE,

29:07.246 --> 29:08.914
BUT THIS IS HOMELAND SECURITY

29:08.955 --> 29:11.375
SPEC OPS LEADER

29:08.955 --> 29:11.375
ELAINE DELACOURT.

29:11.417 --> 29:13.627
You're not fooling anyone.

29:13.669 --> 29:16.714
I'M JUST SAYING.

29:16.755 --> 29:17.923
COME ON.

29:26.932 --> 29:28.350
LOOK, LOOK.

29:47.869 --> 29:49.829
HOW YOU LIKE ME NOW?

29:55.753 --> 29:58.213
-ALL TEAMS, STAND DOWN!

29:55.753 --> 29:58.213
-STAND DOWN!

29:58.255 --> 29:59.757
GOT A MAN INSIDE.

30:04.428 --> 30:05.887
WHAT'S UP?

30:08.766 --> 30:10.809
[ WHISTLES ]

30:10.850 --> 30:12.728
YOU STILL WITH US?

30:12.770 --> 30:15.522
[ GASPING ]

30:15.564 --> 30:17.316
I'M STILL HERE.

30:17.357 --> 30:19.109
HANG IN THERE, COWBOY.

30:20.277 --> 30:22.404
[ Normal voice ]

30:20.277 --> 30:22.404
YIPPEE-KI-YAY, MOTHER--

30:22.446 --> 30:24.114
FOUND IT!

30:25.824 --> 30:27.743
WHAT IS THIS?

30:30.663 --> 30:32.498
IT'S A WATER FILTER.

30:32.539 --> 30:36.084
A VERY  BIG  WATER FILTER,

30:32.539 --> 30:36.084
THE KIND THAT FITS...

30:36.126 --> 30:37.419
IN A DAM.

30:37.461 --> 30:39.505
BUT WHY WOULD A FINANCE GUY --

30:39.546 --> 30:42.466
WHAT WOULD HE BE NEEDING

30:39.546 --> 30:42.466
WATER TECHNOLOGY FOR?

30:42.508 --> 30:44.426
HARDISON, THEY HAVE

30:42.508 --> 30:44.426
THE BUILDING SURROUNDED,

30:44.468 --> 30:46.345
SO WE'RE GONNA GO OUT

30:44.468 --> 30:46.345
THROUGH THE NEXT ONE,

30:46.386 --> 30:48.472
SO MAKE SURE THAT THAT

30:46.386 --> 30:48.472
GLASS WALKWAY IS UNLOCKED.

30:48.514 --> 30:50.015
SOPHIE,

30:48.514 --> 30:50.015
I HOPE YOU GOT US A RIDE.

30:50.056 --> 30:51.183
I'm on it.

30:51.224 --> 30:54.102
FOUND LUCILLE

30:51.224 --> 30:54.102
EXACTLY WHERE WE LEFT HER.

30:54.144 --> 30:55.688
[ ENGINE REVS, TIRES SCREECH ]

30:55.729 --> 30:57.314
SOPHIE'S ON HER WAY.

30:57.356 --> 30:58.940
GOT THIS OFF ONE OF THE GOONS.

30:58.982 --> 31:01.276
LOOK AT THE LAST INCOMING CALL.

31:01.318 --> 31:02.820
[ BEEP ]

31:01.318 --> 31:02.820
ROCKFORD, ILLINOIS.

31:02.861 --> 31:05.280
THAT MEAN ANYTHING TO YOU?

31:05.322 --> 31:07.449
-ALL RIGHT, PHASE 2 IS READY.

31:05.322 --> 31:07.449
-ALL RIGHT, HERE WE GO.

31:07.491 --> 31:10.118
[ Boston accent ] HEY, PAL,

31:10.160 --> 31:11.870
STAY AWAY

31:10.160 --> 31:11.870
FROM THE WEST ENTRANCE.

31:11.911 --> 31:13.288
They're heading there now,

31:13.330 --> 31:14.790
and they're gonna shoot

31:13.330 --> 31:14.790
their way out.

31:14.832 --> 31:16.458
YOU CAN'T DO THIS ON YOUR OWN.

31:16.500 --> 31:17.668
COWBOY?

31:17.710 --> 31:19.795
-Cowboy!

31:17.710 --> 31:19.795
-[ Normal voice ] WHAT?

31:19.837 --> 31:22.506
HE'S...FROM BOSTON.

31:22.548 --> 31:25.718
MOTION SENSORS ON THE WEST

31:22.548 --> 31:25.718
ENTRANCE ARE GOING BERSERK!

31:25.759 --> 31:28.303
EVERYONE TO

31:25.759 --> 31:28.303
THE WEST ENTRANCE NOW!

31:28.345 --> 31:30.639
NEGATIVE.

31:28.345 --> 31:30.639
NOT UNTIL WE HAVE ASCERTAINED --

31:30.681 --> 31:32.516
POWELL, YOU GET BACK HERE!

31:32.558 --> 31:33.726
THAT IS AN ORDER!

31:33.767 --> 31:36.603
MY MAN IS NOT

31:33.767 --> 31:36.603
AN ACCEPTABLE LOSS.

31:36.645 --> 31:38.021
MOVE IN!

31:38.063 --> 31:40.940
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

32:12.138 --> 32:15.183
[ WHIRRING ]

32:23.734 --> 32:25.318
I.E.D.!

32:33.619 --> 32:36.538
OKAY, SOPHIE'S

32:33.619 --> 32:36.538
PULLING AROUND NOW.

32:36.580 --> 32:39.750
THIS BACK STREET

32:36.580 --> 32:39.750
SHOULD BE COMPLETELY...

32:41.251 --> 32:42.878
EMPTY.

32:42.920 --> 32:46.632
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

32:46.673 --> 32:48.091
EXCUSE ME.

32:52.888 --> 32:54.306
HEY, HEY, YOU, WHAT'S GOING ON?

32:54.347 --> 32:55.432
FREE MONEY, MAN.

32:55.474 --> 32:57.183
SOME GUY JUST CALLED

32:55.474 --> 32:57.183
THE RADIO STATION,

32:57.225 --> 32:59.686
SAYS HE'S GONNA THROW

32:57.225 --> 32:59.686
A MILLION BUCKS OFF THE ROOF.

32:59.728 --> 33:01.187
[ SIGHS ]

33:01.229 --> 33:02.397
WHERE'S MY FATHER?

33:02.439 --> 33:05.400
WHAT? HE WAS RIGHT HERE.

33:05.442 --> 33:07.235
HE HAS THE PATENT.

33:07.277 --> 33:09.321
CALLER FROM ALEXANDRIA,

33:09.362 --> 33:12.073
WHAT'S YOUR PLAN TO GIVE THIS

33:09.362 --> 33:12.073
COUNTRY BACK TO THE PEOPLE?

33:12.115 --> 33:14.952
WELL, GOVERNMENT

33:12.115 --> 33:14.952
STOLE MY PATENT,

33:14.993 --> 33:17.078
SO I STOLE $1 MILLION

33:14.993 --> 33:17.078
FROM THE I.R.S.,

33:17.120 --> 33:19.038
AND I'M GONNA THROW IT

33:17.120 --> 33:19.038
OFF THE ROOF

33:19.080 --> 33:21.082
OF THE PATENT BUILDING

33:19.080 --> 33:21.082
IN 10 MINUTES.

33:21.124 --> 33:22.459
WHAT THE HELL JUST HAPPENED?

33:22.501 --> 33:24.795
WHAT JUST HAPPENED IS

33:22.501 --> 33:24.795
A 70-YEAR-OLD WITH A RADIO

33:24.837 --> 33:26.045
JUST CREATED A FLASH MOB.

33:26.087 --> 33:27.172
YOUR DAD DOUBLE-CROSSED US?

33:27.213 --> 33:28.214
YES, HE DID.

33:28.256 --> 33:30.091
COME ON!

33:30.133 --> 33:31.426
WE HAVE TO GO!

33:31.468 --> 33:32.636
NATE.

33:37.641 --> 33:40.560
SOMEBODY'S MESSING

33:37.641 --> 33:40.560
WITH YOUR GAME, NATE.

33:40.602 --> 33:43.271
LATIMER -- HE MIGHT BE THE FRONT

33:40.602 --> 33:43.271
GUY, BUT THIS AIN'T HIS STYLE.

33:43.313 --> 33:44.773
GOT THIS OFF ONE OF THE GOONS.

33:44.815 --> 33:46.191
LOOK AT THE LAST INCOMING CALL.

33:46.232 --> 33:47.818
[ BEEP ]

33:46.232 --> 33:47.818
ROCKFORD, ILLINOIS.

33:47.860 --> 33:49.068
THAT MEAN ANYTHING TO YOU?

33:50.153 --> 33:52.405
I KNOW WHO'S BEHIND THIS.

33:52.447 --> 33:55.993
WE NEED TO FIND MY FATHER FAST.

33:56.034 --> 33:57.577
[ SIGHS ]

34:01.080 --> 34:03.291
HE CALLED THE RADIO STATION.

34:01.080 --> 34:03.291
SEE IF YOU CAN GET A TRACE.

34:03.333 --> 34:05.168
WHERE DO YOU THINK HE'S GONE?

34:05.210 --> 34:07.212
WHERE?

34:05.210 --> 34:07.212
DON'T YOU MEAN  WHEN?

34:12.718 --> 34:15.888
[ BEEPING ]

34:17.848 --> 34:20.350
NOW, WHY WOULD HE GO BACK

34:17.848 --> 34:20.350
TO 1962?

34:20.392 --> 34:21.184
DON'T ENCOURAGE HER.

34:21.226 --> 34:22.394
WHAT IS THAT?

34:22.435 --> 34:23.770
IT'S A BOW TIE.

34:23.812 --> 34:25.313
BOW TIES ARE COOL.

34:25.355 --> 34:26.648
SHOULDN'T WE BE DOING THIS

34:25.355 --> 34:26.648
ON THE ROAD?

34:26.690 --> 34:28.233
I WOULDN'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

34:28.274 --> 34:30.861
I THINK THE FEDS ARE GONNA FIND

34:28.274 --> 34:30.861
WHO THEY WERE LOOKING FOR.

34:38.201 --> 34:41.747
RIGHT ON, COWBOY. RIGHT ON.

34:41.788 --> 34:43.540
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

34:43.582 --> 34:45.458
OKAY, GUYS, GUYS.

34:45.500 --> 34:47.669
DAD! LISTEN, WHERE ARE YOU?

34:47.711 --> 34:49.462
YOU HAVE NO IDEA

34:47.711 --> 34:49.462
WHO YOU'RE UP AGAINST.

34:49.504 --> 34:51.673
THAT'S NEVER STOPPED ME BEFORE.

34:51.715 --> 34:52.966
YEAH, OKAY.

34:51.715 --> 34:52.966
NOW, HERE'S THE THING, DAD --

34:53.008 --> 34:55.301
NOW YOU JUST SIT BACK,

34:53.008 --> 34:55.301
AND BEFORE YOU KNOW IT,

34:55.343 --> 34:57.220
WE'RE GONNA BE TOSSING BACK

34:55.343 --> 34:57.220
A FEW...

34:57.262 --> 34:58.931
-a couple of free men.

34:57.262 --> 34:58.931
-DAD!

34:58.972 --> 35:00.223
NOW, LISTEN TO ME. IF YOU --

34:58.972 --> 35:00.223
[ CLICK ]

35:00.265 --> 35:01.892
ALL RIGHT,

35:00.265 --> 35:01.892
DID YOU GET A LOCATION?

35:01.934 --> 35:04.185
I GOT SOMEPLACE CLOSE

35:01.934 --> 35:04.185
TO THE BALTIMORE WATERFRONT,

35:04.227 --> 35:06.229
BUT IF I PING IT OFF THE TOWERS,

35:04.227 --> 35:06.229
I CAN GET A LITTLE CLOSER.

35:06.271 --> 35:07.773
IT'S JUST GONNA

35:06.271 --> 35:07.773
TAKE ME SOME TIME.

35:07.814 --> 35:09.942
ALL RIGHT, ELIOT, GET US THERE.

35:50.231 --> 35:52.651
WHERE'S THE $2 MILLION?

35:52.692 --> 35:55.112
WHERE'S THE PATENT?

35:57.238 --> 35:58.991
YOU DIDN'T HEAR ME?!

36:09.960 --> 36:11.628
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

36:14.297 --> 36:15.924
OKAY, THERE IT IS.

36:14.297 --> 36:15.924
THERE'S THE PING.

36:15.966 --> 36:18.093
IT'S THE WAREHOUSE DISTRICT

36:15.966 --> 36:18.093
BY THE SHIPPING DOCKS.

36:18.135 --> 36:20.261
WE GOT A 600-FOOT RADIUS.

36:18.135 --> 36:20.261
THAT'S AS CLOSE AS I CAN GET.

36:20.303 --> 36:22.764
-NOT ENOUGH.

36:20.303 --> 36:22.764
-WELL, IT'S EITHER ONE OF

36:20.303 --> 36:22.764
THESE THREE WAREHOUSES --

36:22.806 --> 36:24.307
16, 21, OR A7.

36:24.349 --> 36:25.809
YEAH, OKAY, LISTEN,

36:24.349 --> 36:25.809
I NEED OWNERSHIP RECORDS

36:25.851 --> 36:26.810
FOR ALL OF THEM, OKAY,

36:25.851 --> 36:26.810
RIGHT AWAY.

36:26.852 --> 36:27.811
HEY, ELIOT, COME ON.

36:27.853 --> 36:29.187
DRIVE, DRIVE. LET'S GO.

36:29.228 --> 36:31.606
IT'S NOT MY FAULT, MAN.

36:29.228 --> 36:31.606
IT'S NOT MY CHALLENGER.

36:43.702 --> 36:46.872
THE PATENT, OLD MAN?

36:46.913 --> 36:51.710
DEAL IS...$2 MILLION...

36:53.003 --> 36:54.838
...AND MY SON'S LIFE.

36:54.880 --> 36:57.340
YEAH, SO, WHERE  IS  NATE?

36:57.382 --> 37:00.468
HE'S SAFE, AND I WANT

36:57.382 --> 37:00.468
TO KEEP IT THAT WAY.

37:00.510 --> 37:03.429
A DEAL'S A DEAL.

37:20.613 --> 37:23.449
[ Speed-dialing ]

37:23.491 --> 37:27.079
WE HAVE A SITUATION.

37:27.120 --> 37:29.831
NOPE. HE DIDN'T SHOW.

37:31.958 --> 37:35.253
UM...WELL, LOOK,

37:31.958 --> 37:35.253
THIS IS ALL I GOT --

37:35.294 --> 37:36.462
NO NAMES BUT I GOT COMPANIES.

37:36.504 --> 37:37.964
NO, THAT'S IT.

37:36.504 --> 37:37.964
THAT'S IT RIGHT THERE.

37:38.006 --> 37:39.049
BUILDING 21.

37:39.091 --> 37:40.508
TOBIN-CASEY?

37:39.091 --> 37:40.508
THEY MAKE FISHING REELS.

37:40.550 --> 37:42.844
NO, IT'S JUST A SHELL COMPANY

37:40.550 --> 37:42.844
THAT HE OWNS.

37:42.886 --> 37:44.387
-ELIOT, HOW MUCH LONGER?

37:42.886 --> 37:44.387
-FOUR MINUTES.

37:44.429 --> 37:46.598
OKAY, MAKE IT TWO.

37:46.639 --> 37:49.308
[ Speed-dialing, ringing ]

37:49.350 --> 37:52.353
ALL RIGHT, PLEASE ANSWER.

37:49.350 --> 37:52.353
COME ON.

37:52.395 --> 37:55.190
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

38:06.492 --> 38:07.869
YEAH?

38:07.911 --> 38:10.288
LISTEN, THIS IS A SETUP.

38:10.329 --> 38:11.664
[ COUGHS ]

38:11.706 --> 38:13.875
YOU DON'T THINK I KNOW A SETUP

38:11.706 --> 38:13.875
WHEN I SEE IT?

38:13.917 --> 38:15.127
LATIMER DOUBLE-CROSSED ME.

38:15.168 --> 38:16.211
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

38:16.253 --> 38:17.503
THIS IS NOT ABOUT LATIMER,

38:16.253 --> 38:17.503
ALL RIGHT?

38:17.545 --> 38:18.630
I NEED YOU TO LISTEN

38:17.545 --> 38:18.630
VERY CAREFULLY.

38:18.671 --> 38:19.714
I NEED YOU TO FOCUS.

38:19.756 --> 38:21.800
OH, MAYBE THIS IS

38:19.756 --> 38:21.800
ONE OF THOSE THINGS

38:21.841 --> 38:24.302
THAT YOU WERE RIGHT ABOUT

38:21.841 --> 38:24.302
SO MANY OF THE TIME.

38:24.343 --> 38:26.638
THINGS ARE MORE COMPLICATED

38:24.343 --> 38:26.638
THAN THEY SEEM.

38:26.679 --> 38:28.014
OKAY, JUST WALK OUT

38:26.679 --> 38:28.014
OF THE BUILDING.

38:28.056 --> 38:29.724
START WALKING OUT OF

38:28.056 --> 38:29.724
THE BUILDING RIGHT NOW VERY --

38:29.766 --> 38:30.892
JUST -- JUST START GOING, OKAY?

38:30.934 --> 38:33.645
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

38:33.686 --> 38:35.272
I GOT IT.

38:33.686 --> 38:35.272
IT'S UP HERE AT THE END.

38:44.197 --> 38:45.991
NO, YOU STAY OUT.

38:44.197 --> 38:45.991
DON'T COME IN HERE.

38:46.032 --> 38:47.826
I'm your father.

38:46.032 --> 38:47.826
I'm telling you not to --

38:47.867 --> 38:48.952
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

38:48.994 --> 38:50.411
YOU HAVE TO GET OUT OF

38:48.994 --> 38:50.411
THE BUILDING NOW!

38:50.453 --> 38:51.621
Okay?

38:51.663 --> 38:52.872
IT'S THE FIRST TIME

38:51.663 --> 38:52.872
I'VE BEEN ABLE

38:52.914 --> 38:53.915
TO DO SOME OF THESE THINGS --

38:53.957 --> 38:55.000
the father things.

38:55.041 --> 38:56.417
LISTEN, LISTEN,

38:55.041 --> 38:56.417
IF YOU DON'T GET --

38:56.459 --> 38:58.503
OKAY, OKAY, WE'RE --

38:56.459 --> 38:58.503
WE'RE PULLING UP RIGHT NOW.

38:58.544 --> 39:00.255
I NEED YOU TO WALK OUT

38:58.544 --> 39:00.255
OF THE BUILDING NOW, OKAY?

39:00.297 --> 39:02.090
YOU JUST TELL STORIES.

39:02.132 --> 39:03.967
Tell them stories about me.

39:04.009 --> 39:05.510
NO, NO, NO!

39:04.009 --> 39:05.510
GET -- GET OUT!

39:05.551 --> 39:07.512
I'M COMING IN

39:05.551 --> 39:07.512
TO GET YOU RIGHT NOW!

39:07.553 --> 39:10.598
Tell them -- Tell them...

39:10.640 --> 39:13.977
HOW MUCH JIMMY FORD

39:10.640 --> 39:13.977
LOVES HIS SON.

39:46.009 --> 39:48.845
NATE!

40:24.130 --> 40:25.298
NATE!

40:29.635 --> 40:31.346
NATE.

40:39.271 --> 40:41.064
CAN YOU HEAR ME?

41:30.280 --> 41:32.282
[ BEEP ]
